@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.84
    v0 = (0.20 * ((v1 + 0.96 - tmp + 0.88) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.24)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.35)))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.65)
    v0 = ((0.30 - wp.cos(v0 + 0.46)) / wp.exp((v0 + 0.75 - v0 + 0.93)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
